OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772647567
OL,3,CStarmer to face MPs after Trump
OL,4,Cclaimed he was 'no Churchill' in Iran
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FOn Tuesday, the Prime Minister
OL,8,Fmeanwhile announced Britain would send
OL,9,FHMS Dragon, one of the Royal Navy's
OL,10,Fsix Type 45 air defence destroyers, to
OL,11,Fdefend Cyprus after RAF Akrotiri was
OL,12,Fhit by a drone.
OL,14,FThe war between Iran and the USA, now
OL,15,Fin its fifth day, will likely dominate
OL,16,Fthe agenda when Sir Keir enters the
OL,17,FCommons at noon on Wednesday for Prime
OL,18,FMinister's Questions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772647567
OL,3,CStarmer to face MPs after Trump
OL,4,Cclaimed he was 'no Churchill' in Iran
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FMr Trump has said he is "not happy"
OL,8,Fwith the UK after it did not initially
OL,9,Fallow the US to use its bases for
OL,10,Fstrikes on Iran, later adding in the
OL,11,FOval Office: "This is not Winston
OL,12,FChurchill that we're dealing with."
OL,14,FDowning Street has insisted the US
OL,15,Fremains a "staunch" ally despite the
OL,16,Frepeated broadsides from Mr Trump.
OL,26,@oD@YOUoD@cO]sD@NOUtD@cO]wD@KOUwD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772647567
OL,3,CStarmer to face MPs after Trump
OL,4,Cclaimed he was 'no Churchill' in Iran
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FSir Keir decided on Sunday that UK
OL,8,Fbases including the joint UK-US Diego
OL,9,FGarcia site in the Chagos Islands and
OL,10,FRAF Fairford in Gloucestershire could
OL,11,Fbe used in the conflict, but only so
OL,12,Fthe US can strike defensively to
OL,13,Fprotect countries being targeted by
OL,14,FTehran.
OL,16,FHMS Dragon is being readied to depart
OL,17,Ffor the Mediterranean, and will be
OL,18,Faccompanied by two Wildcat helicopters
OL,19,Fequipped with so-called "drone
OL,20,Fbusting" Martlet missiles, so it can
OL,21,Fprotect Britain's bases in Cyprus.
OL,26,@{D@YOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
