PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772647567
OL,3,CStarmer to face MPs after Trump
OL,4,Cclaimed he was 'no Churchill' in Iran
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FThe warship, which is emblazoned with
OL,8,Fthe Welsh red dragon on its prow, was
OL,9,Fpictured on Tuesday night at the Upper
OL,10,FHarbour Ammunition Facility (UHAF) in
OL,11,FPortsmouth harbour.
OL,13,FElsewhere, Foreign Secretary Yvette
OL,14,FCooper has confirmed that a Government
OL,15,Fcharter flight will take off from
OL,16,FMuscat, Oman, "in the coming days" to
OL,17,Fbring vulnerable British nationals
OL,18,Fback.
OL,26,@xD@OOUxD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
