PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772647567
OL,3,CStarmer to face MPs after Trump
OL,4,Cclaimed he was 'no Churchill' in Iran
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FSome 130,000 Britons have registered
OL,8,Ftheir presence in the Middle East with
OL,9,Fthe Foreign Office amid evacuation
OL,10,Fplanning.
OL,12,FA handful of commercial flights are
OL,13,Falready bringing thousands of stranded
OL,14,FBritons back to the UK, but the vast
OL,15,Fmajority of departures from the region
OL,16,Fhave been cancelled because of
OL,17,Fwidespread airspace closures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
