OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772647567
OL,3,CStarmer to face MPs after Trump
OL,4,Cclaimed he was 'no Churchill' in Iran
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FMr Trump has indicated the US military
OL,8,Fcould start escorting oil tankers as
OL,9,Fthey travel through the narrow strait
OL,10,Fof Hormuz, in order to defend them
OL,11,Ffrom Iranian attacks and contain the
OL,12,Fsoaring energy prices triggered by the
OL,13,Fwar.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
